  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Sync peer management in Eth2.0 requires particular features such as \r\n- Ban peers and don't let them connect to us\r\n- Don't connect to peers that have ban us\r\n- Reverse both actions after some time (TTL/decay for bans/scoring)\r\n- Limit connections per peer\r\n- Handle autoDial with minPeer and maxPeers, not connections\r\n\r\nConsider the dev cost of doing peer management ourselves instead of relying in libp2p connection manager\r\n\r\nCC: @wemeetagain ",
